    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You touch a creature, giving it some of the power of a ghoul king. The target gains the following benefits for the duration:<ul><li>Its Armor Class increases by 2, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>When it uses the Attack action to make a melee weapon attack or a ranged weapon attack, it can make one additional attack of the same kind.</li><li>It is immune to necrotic damage and radiant damage.</li><li>It can’t be reduced to less than 1 hit point.</li><br><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a 9th-level spell slot, the spell lasts for 10 minutes and doesn’t require concentration.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
